Create Plan 5 - "Services Section"
Plan Name: "Services Overview Cards"
Plan Description:
Create an engaging services section with animated cards highlighting
the main service offerings.

Tasks:
Task 1: Services Data

Create lib/services-data.ts:
- Array of 3-4 services
- Each: title, description, icon name (from lucide-react)
- Examples: Custom Metalwork, Woodworking, Welding & Fabrication, Design Consultation

Task 2: Service Card Component

Create components/sections/Services/ServiceCard.tsx:
- Card with hover effect (lift/scale)
- Icon at top (lucide-react, bronze color)
- Title (bold, white)
- Description (steel gray)
- Subtle border or shadow
- Smooth transitions

Task 3: Services Section
Create components/sections/Services.tsx:
- Section heading: "What We Do"
- Grid of ServiceCard components
- 2 cols tablet, 3 desktop
- Scroll-triggered fade-in animations (Framer Motion viewport)
- Responsive spacing


Task 4: Add to Homepage

Update app/page.tsx:
- Add Services section after Portfolio